      <title>Arm 与高通的芯片之争升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-23/arm-escalates-chip-feud-with-qualcomm-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Arm 即将废除与长期合作伙伴高通的芯片许可协议，此举可能会阻碍一些智能手机供应链。Bernstein Research 高级分析师 Stacy Rasgon 与 Ed Ludlow 一起在“彭博科技”节目中讨论这一问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-23/arm-escalates-chip-feud-with-qualcomm-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:29:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jelena McWilliams 关于 Synapse 案件的最新进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-23/jelena-mcwilliams-update-on-synapse-s-case-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前联邦存款保险公司 (FDIC) 主席 Jelena McWilliams 于 5 月被任命为 Synapse 破产案的第 11 章受托人，并试图追回和分配 Synapse 客户资金。她在接受 Sonali Basak 和 Tim Stenovec 在“彭博加密货币”节目采访时介绍了该案的最新进展。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-23/jelena-mcwilliams-update-on-synapse-s-case-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:13:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西门子正在洽谈收购软件集团 Altair</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/siemens-in-talks-to-buy-software-group-altair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，西门子股份公司正在就收购软件制造商 Altair Engineering Inc. 的潜在交易进行谈判，这将成为该公司有史以来最大的收购之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/siemens-in-talks-to-buy-software-group-altair</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jelena McWilliams 谈加密货币预测市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-23/jelena-mcwilliams-on-crypto-prediction-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前 FDIC 主席兼 Cravath, Swaine &amp; Moore 合伙人 Jelena McWilliams 讨论了与美国大选相关的基于加密货币的预测市场，并表示大多数预测最终都会在某种程度上出现缺陷。她与 Sonali Basak 和 Tim Stenovec 在“Bloomberg Crypto”节目中进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-23/jelena-mcwilliams-on-crypto-prediction-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cox 预计 11 月在西班牙进行 IPO，公司正在等待监管部门批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/cox-s-spain-ipo-expected-in-november-as-regulatory-nod-awaited</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Cox Abg Group SA 预计将于下个月确定其首次公开募股的定价，目前正在等待西班牙证券监管机构批准启动股票出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/cox-s-spain-ipo-expected-in-november-as-regulatory-nod-awaited</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 18:57:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
